'''Umudugudu wa Umusambi''', 

washinzwe n’ishyirahamwe ryita ku nyamaswa zo mu Rwanda ziyobowe n’umuvuzi w’amatungo Olivier Nsengimana,  ni igishanga cyagaruwe i [[Kigali]], mu [[Rwanda]] kikaba ubuhungiro bw’imisambi irenga 50 itagira ingano ( ''Balearica regulorum'' ) yakuwe mu bucuruzi butemewe bw'amatungo. 

Izi nyoni zamugaye kubera ubunyage kandi ntizishobora kurekurwa mumashyamba. Umudugudu w'Umusambi cyangwa Umusambi Village mu ndimi zamahanga uha izo nyoni ahantu hakurura imbaraga zishobora guhura na kamere. 

Nsengimana yatangiye umushinga w'Umudugudu w'umusambi mu mwaka wa 2014.  Icyari kigamijwe kwari uguhagarika ubucuruzi butemewe bwa crane cg imisambi, guteza imbere ubukangurambaga, no kurekura crane(imisambi) myinshi yajyanywe mu gasozi, muri [[Pariki y'Akagera|Parike ya Akagera]] .

Muri uwo mushinga, basanze crane nyinshi zamugaye kubera gufungwa kwazo. Ibi bikunze guhuzwa no gufata no gutwara, ndetse no gukata amababa kugirango birinde kuguruka, bishobora kugenda nabi cyane iyo bikozwe nta buhanga.  

